HRESULT OESTORE::IOEFolderManager::ActivateGlobalNotification (  ) 

Activate the IOEFolderManagerEvents::OnNewMessage notification.
You need to activate it explicitly because the activation takes some time.

HRESULT OESTORE::IOEFolderManager::GetNextFolder ( [out, retval] OEFolder **  folder  ) 

Get next folder. This function returns the first child folder of the previous object if any, the sibling folder if any or the parent sibling. If the previous was the last folder, it returns NULL.
